---
import "../styles/tokens.css";
import "../styles/landing.css";
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>McCoy — Scan your MCP servers. Auto-fix what's broken.</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="McCoy scans live MCP tool surfaces for deterministic security issues, advises with GPT-5.6, and auto-fixes with Codex."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/">mccoy</a>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="/">Docs</a>
          <a href="/quickstart/">Quickstart</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/nitishagar/mccoy">GitHub</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <h1>Scan your MCP servers.<br />Auto-fix what's broken.</h1>
        <p class="subhead">
          McCoy connects to any MCP server, runs eight deterministic security rules over its tool
          surface, annotates the ambiguous ones with GPT-5.6, and drives Codex to patch what it
          can — re-scanning until clean.
        </p>
        <div class="ctas">
          <a class="cta primary" href="/install/">Install</a>
          <a class="cta" href="/quickstart/">Quickstart</a>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-demo">
          <div class="terminal-title">mccoy scan fixtures/vuln_server/server.py</div>
<pre><code>HIGH MCC001 unsafe_lookup: Description contains an instruction-injection marker.
MEDIUM MCC002 unsafe_lookup: Input schema does not forbid unknown properties.
HIGH MCC003 unsafe_lookup: Tool definition exposes a secret-looking reference.
MEDIUM MCC005 unsafe_lookup: Tool description advertises a 0.0.0.0 bind.
...
12 finding(s) across 4 tool(s)
exit=2</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <span>McCoy — built with Codex and GPT-5.6 for OpenAI Build Week 2026.</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/nitishagar/mccoy">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
